Package: querychat
Title: Filter and Query Data Frames in 'shiny' Using an LLM Chat Interface
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Garrick", "Aden-Buie", , "garrick@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre"),
